                <h2>2、上传填写好的商品资料</h2>
                <div class="upload m-b">
                    <div>
                        <button onclick="app.shopsp.import_goods();" id="upload-file" class="btn w-xs btn-info box-shawn" type="button">上传</button>

                        <span class="desc">（请选择excel文件@*，一次最多上传 2000 条数据*@）</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
